    <item>
      <title>How our new phishing report button integrates directly with Microsoft Defender</title>
      <link>https://www.cyberpilot.io/cyberpilot-blog/report-phishing-and-get-the-secure-behaviour</link>
      <description>&lt;div class="hs-featured-image-wrapper"&gt; 
 &lt;a href="https://www.cyberpilot.io/cyberpilot-blog/report-phishing-and-get-the-secure-behaviour" title="" class="hs-featured-image-link"&gt; &lt;img src="https://www.cyberpilot.io/hubfs/New%20Platform%20Feature%20-%20Reporting%20Phishing.png" alt="How our new phishing report button integrates directly with Microsoft Defender" class="hs-featured-image" style="width:auto !important; max-width:50%; float:left; margin:0 15px 15px 0;"&gt; &lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Our newest &lt;a href="https://www.cyberpilot.io/phishing-training" style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;phishing training&lt;/a&gt; feature takes simulation insights to a whole new level. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;CyberPilot is one of the first providers to fully integrate the data from both our platform and Microsoft Outlook. With this integration, you can see exactly which users took the &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;right&lt;/span&gt; action by using Outlook's built-in "Report Phishing" button.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This powerful addition to our phishing simulation reports gives you a more comprehensive view of your organisation's phishing resilien&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;ce. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded>&lt;div class="hs-featured-image-wrapper"&gt; 
 &lt;a href="https://www.cyberpilot.io/cyberpilot-blog/report-phishing-and-get-the-secure-behaviour" title="" class="hs-featured-image-link"&gt; &lt;img src="https://www.cyberpilot.io/hubfs/New%20Platform%20Feature%20-%20Reporting%20Phishing.png" alt="How our new phishing report button integrates directly with Microsoft Defender" class="hs-featured-image" style="width:auto !important; max-width:50%; float:left; margin:0 15px 15px 0;"&gt; &lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/div&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Our newest &lt;a href="https://www.cyberpilot.io/phishing-training" style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;phishing training&lt;/a&gt; feature takes simulation insights to a whole new level. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;CyberPilot is one of the first providers to fully integrate the data from both our platform and Microsoft Outlook. With this integration, you can see exactly which users took the &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;right&lt;/span&gt; action by using Outlook's built-in "Report Phishing" button.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This powerful addition to our phishing simulation reports gives you a more comprehensive view of your organisation's phishing resilien&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;ce. &lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  
